---
const prepareIcons = [
  { name: 'Slack', icon: '/images/integrations/slack.png' },
  { name: 'Google Workspace', icon: '/images/integrations/google-workspace.png' },
  { name: 'Linear', icon: '/images/integrations/linear.png' },
  { name: 'Microsoft Teams', icon: '/images/integrations/microsoft-teams.png' },
  { name: 'Google Meet', icon: '/images/integrations/google-meet.png' },
  { name: 'Asana', icon: '/images/integrations/asana.png' },
  { name: 'Jira', icon: '/images/integrations/jira.png' },
];
---

<section id="how-it-works" class="py-20 md:py-32 bg-white relative overflow-hidden z-10">
  <!-- Subtle gradient tinge on edges -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(ellipse_at_0%_50%,rgba(184,207,255,0.3),transparent_50%),radial-gradient(ellipse_at_100%_50%,rgba(184,207,255,0.3),transparent_50%)] pointer-events-none" aria-hidden="true"></div>

  <div class="container-ip relative">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <p class="text-ip-navy/60 text-[30px] mb-6 font-display">How does it work?</p>
      <h2 class="font-display text-4xl md:text-6xl tracking-tight mb-8 text-ip-navy">
        It listens. It updates. You move on.
      </h2>
      <p class="text-ip-navy/60 text-lg leading-relaxed max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        In Parallel joins your meetings, picks up decisions, ownership changes, and new priorities — then updates your plan and connected tools. No one has to remember what changed or write it down.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="relative max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <!-- Dashed border container decoration -->
      <img src="/images/sections/hiw-border.png" alt="" width="1025" height="828" class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-contain pointer-events-none" aria-hidden="true" />

      <!-- Learn label — left side with right-pointing arrow -->
      <div class="hidden md:flex absolute left-0 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 -translate-x-full items-center" aria-hidden="true">
        <span class="bg-ip-navy text-white text-sm font-display px-4 py-2">Learn</span>
        <svg width="8" height="34" viewBox="0 0 8 34" fill="none" class="shrink-0">
          <polygon points="0,0 8,17 0,34" class="fill-ip-navy" />
        </svg>
      </div>

      <!-- Replan label — right side with left-pointing arrow -->
      <div class="hidden md:flex absolute right-0 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 translate-x-full items-center" aria-hidden="true">
        <svg width="8" height="34" viewBox="0 0 8 34" fill="none" class="shrink-0">
          <polygon points="8,0 0,17 8,34" class="fill-ip-navy" />
        </svg>
        <span class="bg-ip-navy text-white text-sm font-display px-4 py-2">Plan</span>
      </div>

      <div class="relative py-12 space-y-12">
        <!-- Step 1: Prepare -->
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-10 h-10 bg-ip-navy text-white border border-ip-navy rounded-full text-sm font-display mb-4">
            1
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-display text-3xl md:text-4xl mb-4 text-ip-navy">Before</h3>
          <p class="text-ip-navy/60 text-base max-w-lg mx-auto">
            Before each meeting, you see what changed, what's at risk, and what needs a decision. You walk in prepared.
          </p>
          <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-4 mt-6">
            {prepareIcons.map((item) => (
              <img src={item.icon} alt={item.name} width="45" height="45" class="w-[45px] h-[45px] rounded-lg" />
            ))}
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 2: Capture -->
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-10 h-10 bg-ip-navy text-white border border-ip-navy rounded-full text-sm font-display mb-4">
            2
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-display text-3xl md:text-4xl mb-4 text-ip-navy">During</h3>
          <p class="text-ip-navy/60 text-base max-w-lg mx-auto">
            It listens to the meeting and captures every decision, owner change, and commitment — without anyone taking notes.
          </p>
          <!-- Project weekly card -->
          <div class="bg-ip-navy rounded-xl p-8 mt-6 max-w-lg mx-auto text-center">
            <span class="inline-block bg-ip-lime text-ip-navy text-xs font-display px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full">Project weekly</span>
            <div class="ai-thinking-rotator mt-4">
              <p class="text-ip-white-muted text-sm ai-thinking-label">
                <span class="ai-thinking-track">
                  <span class="ai-thinking-item">analysing priorities...</span>
                  <span class="ai-thinking-item">detecting ownership gaps...</span>
                  <span class="ai-thinking-item">scanning for risk...</span>
                  <span class="ai-thinking-item">checking deadline drift...</span>
                  <span class="ai-thinking-item">mapping dependencies...</span>
                  <span class="ai-thinking-item">analysing priorities...</span>
                </span>
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="ai-question-rotator mt-2">
              <p class="text-white font-display ai-question-label">
                <span class="ai-question-track">
                  <span class="ai-question-item">What will miss next 14 days if we change nothing?</span>
                  <span class="ai-question-item">Who owns the blockers no one is talking about?</span>
                  <span class="ai-question-item">Which decisions from last week haven't landed yet?</span>
                  <span class="ai-question-item">Where is the plan drifting from what actually happened?</span>
                  <span class="ai-question-item">What commitments are at risk this sprint?</span>
                  <span class="ai-question-item">What will miss next 14 days if we change nothing?</span>
                </span>
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 3: Update -->
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-10 h-10 bg-ip-navy text-white border border-ip-navy rounded-full text-sm font-display mb-4">
            3
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-display text-3xl md:text-4xl mb-4 text-ip-navy">After</h3>
          <p class="text-ip-navy/60 text-base max-w-lg mx-auto">
            Your plan updates, connected tools sync, and a summary goes out. Nothing for you to do.
          </p>
          <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-4 mt-6">
            <img src="/images/sections/hiw-score.png" alt="Execution score: 82 out of 100" width="254" height="101" class="h-20 md:h-24 w-auto rounded-lg" />
            <img src="/images/sections/hiw-metric-1.png" alt="72% progress — Increase R&D Investment" width="254" height="151" class="h-20 md:h-24 w-auto rounded-lg" />
            <img src="/images/sections/hiw-metric-2.png" alt="96% progress — Grow Residential Market Share" width="254" height="151" class="h-20 md:h-24 w-auto rounded-lg" />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
